title: CLOSE_SEQUENCE_TASK
content:
0x39E72BC99E6360CB0x1A7CEBD0// CloseSequenceTask
void CLOSE_SEQUENCE_TASK(int taskSequenceId);Parameters:taskSequenceId: The task sequence to closeFor an example on how to use this please refer to OPEN_SEQUENCE_TASKNOTEIf you fail to call CLOSE_SEQUENCE_TASK and CLEAR_SEQUENCE_TASK this can get stuck in a broken state until you restart your client.
